text: Inge Keller (15 December 1923 - 6 February 2017) was a German actress. Her career on stage and on movies has for seventy years. She was one of the most well-known performers in the former German Democratic Republic. Keller was known for her roles in The Last Year, Aimée & Jaguar, Council of the Gods, Lola and Billy the Kid, Karla, The Fiancé, and in Woman Doctors. Keller was born on 15 December 1923 in Berlin, Germany. Keller died in a Berlin nursing home on 6 February 2017, aged 93. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1923 births Category:2017 deaths Category:German movie actors Category:German stage actors Category:People from Berlin
